<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Web: designer / developer / problem solver</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Landing Pages"/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Landing Page examples</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Landing Pages</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">It's estimated that 32% of New Zealand businesses still don't have a website. While <a href="http://www.carbonstudios.co.nz/" target="_blank">Carbon</a> was initially set up as primarily a design agency, the success of our website production and the obvious need among small businesses has meant that web design and development is our primary source of client revenue. As such, small, single page (landing pages), websites seem to be the most popular.</p><p>These pages are generally produced in html5, css and jQuery but can incorporate a host of technologies depending on the clients needs. I generally code these from scratch, with the exception of any jQuery plug-ins, within four hours. They are very quickly produced and succeed in providing the client with an online presence.</p><p>I have built many of these sites and for the most part they're all pretty similar. The examples I've presented here are: <a href="http://andersonswanganui.co.nz/" target="_blank">Andersons</a> and <a href="http://www.mcknightandbrown.co.nz/" target="_blank">McKnight & Brown.</a></p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/landingpages/image_01_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/landingpages/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Andersons landing page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/landingpages/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/landingpages/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="McKnight & Brown landing page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>